extends layout

block content
  h1= title
  p Welcome to #[em UserBase] A very simple express site developed and modified from a tutorial on the Mozilla Develepor Network.

  h1 Dynamic content

  if error
    p Error getting dynamic content.
  else
    p The UserBase has the following record counts:

    ul
      li #[strong Users:] !{data.user_count}
      li #[strong Users Online:] !{data.user_instance_online_count}
      li #[strong Probably not something I'd want to be public:] !{data.user_instance_count} 



















